/* link style reference:
style="font-weight:800;color:#4471b7!important;margin: unset; padding-left:0 !important;margin-right:0 !important;"
*/

/* This hides the Title of the Overview tab */
#onetrust-consent-sdk #onetrust-pc-sdk h4{
display:none;
}

/* This hides the Title and toggle for the 2nd tab */
#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-desc-cntr:nth-child(2) .ot-grp-hdr1{
display:none;
}

#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-grp-desc a {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #4471b7;
    text-decoration: none;
    background-color: transparent;
    border: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

/* RETAINING, but these sliders are NOT USED for GENERIC in Kroger Banners because there are no eligible opt-out rights for the generic consumer to exercise */

/* Constructors for Slider */

/* Sider Status Label */
#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-label-status {
    font-size: 1em;
    font-weight: bold;
    position: relative;
    top: 2px;
    display: none;
    padding-right: 5px;
    float: left;
}

/* Slider Bar */
#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-switch {
    FONT-WEIGHT: 100;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 45px;
    height: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 0px;
}

/*Slider Circle */

#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-switch-nob {
    position: absolute;
    cursor: pointer;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-color: #f2f1f1;
    border: none;
    transition: all .2s ease-in 0s;
    -moz-transition: all .2s ease-in 0s;
    -o-transition: all .2s ease-in 0s;
    -webkit-transition: all .2s ease-in 0s;
    border-radius: 45px;
}


#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-switch-nob:before {
    position: absolute;
    content: "";
    height: 30px;
    width: 30px;
    bottom: 1px;
    background-color: #7d7d7d;
    -webkit-transition: .4s;
    border-radius: 100%;
    top: 0px;
    transition: .4s;
}

/* Raises Opt-Out of Sale title to the top, adjusts Slider position */
/* Position the title and toggle: */

#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-grp-hdr1 {
    padding-left: unset;
    width: unset;
    padding-top: 2px;
	padding-right: 2px;
    margin-bottom: unset;
    padding-bottom: unset;
    position: absolute;
	right:0;
}

#onetrust-pc-sdk .ot-desc-cntr {
    position: relative;
}
